		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_13&quot; title=&quot;December 13&quot;&gt;December 13&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 117px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Wojciech Jaruzelski&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Wojciech Jaruzelski&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg/117px-Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;117&quot; height=&quot;167&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg/176px-Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg/234px-Wojciech_Jaruzelski.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;421&quot; data-file-height=&quot;600&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Wojciech Jaruzelski&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1643&quot; title=&quot;1643&quot;&gt;1643&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/First_English_Civil_War&quot; title=&quot;First English Civil War&quot;&gt;First English Civil War&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Roundhead&quot; title=&quot;Roundhead&quot;&gt;Roundhead&lt;/a&gt; forces under &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/William_Waller&quot; title=&quot;William Waller&quot;&gt;Sir William Waller&lt;/a&gt; led &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Alton&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Alton&quot;&gt;a successful surprise attack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; on a winter garrison of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Cavalier&quot; title=&quot;Cavalier&quot;&gt;Royalist&lt;/a&gt; infantry and cavalry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1769&quot; title=&quot;1769&quot;&gt;1769&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Dartmouth_College&quot; title=&quot;Dartmouth College&quot;&gt;Dartmouth College&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, in present-day &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hanover,_New_Hampshire&quot; title=&quot;Hanover, New Hampshire&quot;&gt;Hanover, New Hampshire&lt;/a&gt;, was established by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Royal_charter&quot; title=&quot;Royal charter&quot;&gt;royal charter&lt;/a&gt;, becoming the last university to be founded in the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Thirteen_Colonies&quot; title=&quot;Thirteen Colonies&quot;&gt;Thirteen Colonies&lt;/a&gt; before the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/American_Revolution&quot; title=&quot;American Revolution&quot;&gt;American Revolution&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1981&quot; title=&quot;1981&quot;&gt;1981&lt;/a&gt; – Polish prime minister &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Wojciech_Jaruzelski&quot; title=&quot;Wojciech Jaruzelski&quot;&gt;Wojciech Jaruzelski&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; performed a &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Self-coup&quot; title=&quot;Self-coup&quot;&gt;self-coup&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Martial_law_in_Poland&quot; title=&quot;Martial law in Poland&quot;&gt;declaring martial law&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, suspending the trade union &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Solidarity_(Polish_trade_union)&quot; title=&quot;Solidarity (Polish trade union)&quot;&gt;Solidarity&lt;/a&gt; and imprisoning many of its leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2001&quot; title=&quot;2001&quot;&gt;2001&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Parliament_of_India&quot; title=&quot;Parliament of India&quot;&gt;Parliament of India&lt;/a&gt; was &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2001_Indian_Parliament_attack&quot; title=&quot;2001 Indian Parliament attack&quot;&gt;attacked by five gunmen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, who killed nine people.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2011&quot; title=&quot;2011&quot;&gt;2011&lt;/a&gt; – After murdering a woman at his home, a man &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2011_Li%C3%A8ge_attack&quot; title=&quot;2011 Liège attack&quot;&gt;threw grenades and fired a rifle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; at crowds in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Li%C3%A8ge&quot; title=&quot;Liège&quot;&gt;Liège&lt;/a&gt;, Belgium, killing 6 people and injuring 125 others, before killing himself.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Pope_Callixtus_II&quot; title=&quot;Pope Callixtus II&quot;&gt;Pope Callixtus&amp;#160;II&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1124)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Emily_Carr&quot; title=&quot;Emily Carr&quot;&gt;Emily Carr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1871)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hans-Joachim_Marseille&quot; title=&quot;Hans-Joachim Marseille&quot;&gt;Hans-Joachim Marseille&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1919)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_12&quot; title=&quot;December 12&quot;&gt;December 12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_13&quot; title=&quot;December 13&quot;&gt;December 13&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_14&quot; title=&quot;December 14&quot;&gt;December 14&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
