		<title>On this day: December 14</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20211214000000/en"/>
		<updated>2021-12-14T00:00:00Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_14&quot; title=&quot;December 14&quot;&gt;December 14&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Martyred_Intellectuals_Day&quot; title=&quot;Martyred Intellectuals Day&quot;&gt;Martyred Intellectuals Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Bangladesh (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1971&quot; title=&quot;1971&quot;&gt;1971&lt;/a&gt;); &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Monkey_Day&quot; title=&quot;Monkey Day&quot;&gt;Monkey Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 125px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:TangWenzongAlt.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Emperor Wenzong of Tang&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Emperor Wenzong of Tang&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/TangWenzongAlt.jpg/125px-TangWenzongAlt.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;125&quot; height=&quot;156&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/TangWenzongAlt.jpg/188px-TangWenzongAlt.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/TangWenzongAlt.jpg/250px-TangWenzongAlt.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;276&quot; data-file-height=&quot;345&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Emperor Wenzong of Tang&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/835&quot; title=&quot;835&quot;&gt;835&lt;/a&gt; – In the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Sweet_Dew_incident&quot; title=&quot;Sweet Dew incident&quot;&gt;Sweet Dew incident&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Emperor_Wenzong_of_Tang&quot; title=&quot;Emperor Wenzong of Tang&quot;&gt;Emperor Wenzong&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Tang_dynasty&quot; title=&quot;Tang dynasty&quot;&gt;Tang dynasty&lt;/a&gt; conspired to kill the powerful &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Eunuch&quot; title=&quot;Eunuch&quot;&gt;eunuchs&lt;/a&gt; of the Tang court, but the plot was foiled.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1863&quot; title=&quot;1863&quot;&gt;1863&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/American_Civil_War&quot; title=&quot;American Civil War&quot;&gt;American Civil War&lt;/a&gt;: The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Bean%27s_Station&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Bean&amp;#39;s Station&quot;&gt;Battle of Bean's Station&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, the final battle of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Knoxville_campaign&quot; title=&quot;Knoxville campaign&quot;&gt;Knoxville campaign&lt;/a&gt;, was fought in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Grainger_County,_Tennessee&quot; title=&quot;Grainger County, Tennessee&quot;&gt;Grainger County, Tennessee&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1918&quot; title=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;1918&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1918_United_Kingdom_general_election&quot; title=&quot;1918 United Kingdom general election&quot;&gt;first British general election with female voters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; took place, with women over the age of thirty permitted to vote.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1981&quot; title=&quot;1981&quot;&gt;1981&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Knesset&quot; title=&quot;Knesset&quot;&gt;Knesset&lt;/a&gt; passed the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Golan_Heights_Law&quot; title=&quot;Golan Heights Law&quot;&gt;Golan Heights Law&lt;/a&gt;, extending Israeli &quot;laws, jurisdiction and administration&quot; to the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Golan_Heights&quot; title=&quot;Golan Heights&quot;&gt;Golan Heights&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, effectively &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Annexation&quot; title=&quot;Annexation&quot;&gt;annexing&lt;/a&gt; the territory internationally recognized as part of Syria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1998&quot; title=&quot;1998&quot;&gt;1998&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kosovo_War&quot; title=&quot;Kosovo War&quot;&gt;Kosovo War&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Serbia_and_Montenegro&quot; title=&quot;Serbia and Montenegro&quot;&gt;Yugoslav&lt;/a&gt; forces &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_14,_1998,_Albanian%E2%80%93Yugoslav_border_ambush&quot; title=&quot;December 14, 1998, Albanian–Yugoslav border ambush&quot;&gt;ambushed a group&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kosovo_Liberation_Army&quot; title=&quot;Kosovo Liberation Army&quot;&gt;Kosovo Liberation Army&lt;/a&gt; militants attempting to smuggle weapons into Yugoslavia from Albania.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Niccol%C3%B2_Perotti&quot; title=&quot;Niccolò Perotti&quot;&gt;Niccolò Perotti&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1480)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/DeFord_Bailey&quot; title=&quot;DeFord Bailey&quot;&gt;DeFord Bailey&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1899)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kim_Beazley&quot; title=&quot;Kim Beazley&quot;&gt;Kim Beazley&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1948)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
