&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/546&quot; title=&quot;546&quot;&gt;546&lt;/a&gt; – Led by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Totila&quot; title=&quot;Totila&quot;&gt;Totila&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Ostrogoths&quot; title=&quot;Ostrogoths&quot;&gt;Ostrogoths&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Sack_of_Rome_(546)&quot; title=&quot;Sack of Rome (546)&quot;&gt;sacked Rome&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; after a nearly year-long siege.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1583&quot; title=&quot;1583&quot;&gt;1583&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Cologne_War&quot; title=&quot;Cologne War&quot;&gt;Cologne War&lt;/a&gt;: Forces under &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Ernest_of_Bavaria&quot; title=&quot;Ernest of Bavaria&quot;&gt;Ernest of Bavaria&lt;/a&gt; defeated &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gebhard_Truchsess_von_Waldburg&quot; title=&quot;Gebhard Truchsess von Waldburg&quot;&gt;Gebhard Truchsess von Waldburg&lt;/a&gt;'s troops at the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Siege_of_Godesberg&quot; title=&quot;Siege of Godesberg&quot;&gt;siege of Godesberg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1918&quot; title=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;1918&lt;/a&gt; – About 1,000 demonstrators &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Darwin_rebellion&quot; title=&quot;Darwin rebellion&quot;&gt;marched&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; on &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Government_House,_Darwin&quot; title=&quot;Government House, Darwin&quot;&gt;Government House&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Darwin,_Northern_Territory&quot; title=&quot;Darwin, Northern Territory&quot;&gt;Darwin&lt;/a&gt;, Australia, where they burned an &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Effigy&quot; title=&quot;Effigy&quot;&gt;effigy&lt;/a&gt; of Administrator &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/John_A._Gilruth&quot; title=&quot;John A. Gilruth&quot;&gt;John Gilruth&lt;/a&gt; and demanded his resignation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1951&quot; title=&quot;1951&quot;&gt;1951&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Civil_Rights_Congress&quot; title=&quot;Civil Rights Congress&quot;&gt;Civil Rights Congress&lt;/a&gt; presented a document to the United Nations &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Genocide_Convention&quot; title=&quot;Genocide Convention&quot;&gt;Genocide Convention&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/We_Charge_Genocide&quot; title=&quot;We Charge Genocide&quot;&gt;charging the United States government with genocide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; against &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/African_Americans&quot; title=&quot;African Americans&quot;&gt;African Americans&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1983&quot; title=&quot;1983&quot;&gt;1983&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Provisional_Irish_Republican_Army&quot; title=&quot;Provisional Irish Republican Army&quot;&gt;Provisional Irish Republican Army&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Harrods_bombing&quot; title=&quot;Harrods bombing&quot;&gt;detonated a car bomb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; just outside &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Harrods&quot; title=&quot;Harrods&quot;&gt;Harrods&lt;/a&gt; in London, killing six people and injuring about 90 others.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Nzinga_of_Ndongo_and_Matamba&quot; title=&quot;Nzinga of Ndongo and Matamba&quot;&gt;Nzinga of Ndongo and Matamba&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1663)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Aubrey_Faulkner&quot; title=&quot;Aubrey Faulkner&quot;&gt;Aubrey Faulkner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1881)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Eva_Ekvall&quot; title=&quot;Eva Ekvall&quot;&gt;Eva Ekvall&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;2011)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
