		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_18&quot; title=&quot;December 18&quot;&gt;December 18&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/National_Day_(Qatar)&quot; title=&quot;National Day (Qatar)&quot;&gt;National Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Qatar (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1878&quot; title=&quot;1878&quot;&gt;1878&lt;/a&gt;)
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 140px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e,_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Gaston de Chasseloup-Laubat&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Gaston de Chasseloup-Laubat&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg/140px-Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;140&quot; height=&quot;140&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg/210px-Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg/280px-Le_comte_Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat_sur_Jeantaud_Duc_%C3%A9lectrique_Profil%C3%A9e%2C_recordman_de_vitesse_le_le_4_mars_1899_%C3%A0_Ach%C3%A8res.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;655&quot; data-file-height=&quot;656&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Gaston de Chasseloup-Laubat&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1499&quot; title=&quot;1499&quot;&gt;1499&lt;/a&gt; – Muslims in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Granada&quot; title=&quot;Granada&quot;&gt;Granada&lt;/a&gt; began &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Rebellion_of_the_Alpujarras_(1499%E2%80%931501)&quot; title=&quot;Rebellion of the Alpujarras (1499–1501)&quot;&gt;a rebellion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; against their &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Crown_of_Castile&quot; title=&quot;Crown of Castile&quot;&gt;Castilian&lt;/a&gt; rulers in response to &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Forced_conversions_of_Muslims_in_Spain&quot; title=&quot;Forced conversions of Muslims in Spain&quot;&gt;forced conversions to Catholicism&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1898&quot; title=&quot;1898&quot;&gt;1898&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gaston_de_Chasseloup-Laubat&quot; title=&quot;Gaston de Chasseloup-Laubat&quot;&gt;Gaston de Chasseloup-Laubat&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; set the first official &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Land_speed_record&quot; title=&quot;Land speed record&quot;&gt;land speed record&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, averaging 63.16&amp;#160;km/h (39.245&amp;#160;mph) over 1&amp;#160;km (0.62&amp;#160;mi) in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Ach%C3%A8res,_Yvelines&quot; title=&quot;Achères, Yvelines&quot;&gt;Achères&lt;/a&gt;, France.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1916&quot; title=&quot;1916&quot;&gt;1916&lt;/a&gt; – The French &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Verdun&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Verdun&quot;&gt;defeated German forces&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; around the city of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Verdun&quot; title=&quot;Verdun&quot;&gt;Verdun-sur-Meuse&lt;/a&gt; in northeast France, ending the longest and one of the bloodiest battles in the First World War.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1996&quot; title=&quot;1996&quot;&gt;1996&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Oakland_Unified_School_District&quot; title=&quot;Oakland Unified School District&quot;&gt;school board of Oakland, California&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/African-American_Vernacular_English_and_education&quot; title=&quot;African-American Vernacular English and education&quot;&gt;passed a controversial resolution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; officially declaring &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/African-American_Vernacular_English&quot; title=&quot;African-American Vernacular English&quot;&gt;African-American Vernacular English&lt;/a&gt; to be a separate language or dialect.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Henrietta_Edwards&quot; title=&quot;Henrietta Edwards&quot;&gt;Henrietta Edwards&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1849)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Robert_Moses&quot; title=&quot;Robert Moses&quot;&gt;Robert Moses&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1888)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Noriko_Matsueda&quot; title=&quot;Noriko Matsueda&quot;&gt;Noriko Matsueda&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1971)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
