&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 198px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Cardiff City Hall&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Cardiff City Hall&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg/198px-Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;198&quot; height=&quot;99&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg/297px-Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg/396px-Cardiff_City_Hall_cropped.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;2216&quot; data-file-height=&quot;1108&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Cardiff City Hall&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1955&quot; title=&quot;1955&quot;&gt;1955&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Cardiff&quot; title=&quot;Cardiff&quot;&gt;Cardiff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/City_Hall,_Cardiff&quot; title=&quot;City Hall, Cardiff&quot;&gt;City Hall&lt;/a&gt; pictured)&lt;/i&gt; was recognised as the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Capital_of_Wales&quot; title=&quot;Capital of Wales&quot;&gt;capital of Wales&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1968&quot; title=&quot;1968&quot;&gt;1968&lt;/a&gt; – The first two confirmed murders by the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Zodiac_Killer&quot; title=&quot;Zodiac Killer&quot;&gt;Zodiac Killer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; occurred in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Benicia,_California&quot; title=&quot;Benicia, California&quot;&gt;Benicia, California&lt;/a&gt;, in a case which remains unsolved.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1988&quot; title=&quot;1988&quot;&gt;1988&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/United_Nations_Convention_Against_Illicit_Traffic_in_Narcotic_Drugs_and_Psychotropic_Substances&quot; title=&quot;United Nations Convention Against Illicit Traffic in Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances&quot;&gt;United Nations Convention Against Illicit Traffic in Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; governing international cooperation against the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Illegal_drug_trade&quot; title=&quot;Illegal drug trade&quot;&gt;illegal drug trade&lt;/a&gt; was signed in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Vienna&quot; title=&quot;Vienna&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1995&quot; title=&quot;1995&quot;&gt;1995&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/American_Airlines_Flight_965&quot; title=&quot;American Airlines Flight 965&quot;&gt;American Airlines Flight 965&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; crashed into a mountain in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Buga,_Valle_del_Cauca&quot; title=&quot;Buga, Valle del Cauca&quot;&gt;Buga, Colombia&lt;/a&gt;, killing 151 passengers and 8 crew members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2007&quot; title=&quot;2007&quot;&gt;2007&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Pablo_Picasso&quot; title=&quot;Pablo Picasso&quot;&gt;Pablo Picasso&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Portrait_of_Suzanne_Bloch&quot; title=&quot;Portrait of Suzanne Bloch&quot;&gt;Portrait of Suzanne Bloch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; was stolen from the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Paulo_Museum_of_Art&quot; title=&quot;São Paulo Museum of Art&quot;&gt;São Paulo Museum of Art&lt;/a&gt;, before being recovered about three weeks later.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/John_Bell_(farmer)&quot; title=&quot;John Bell (farmer)&quot;&gt;John Bell&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1820)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kan%27ichi_Asakawa&quot; title=&quot;Kan&amp;#39;ichi Asakawa&quot;&gt;Kan'ichi Asakawa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1873)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Beatrice_Beeby&quot; title=&quot;Beatrice Beeby&quot;&gt;Beatrice Beeby&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1991)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
