		<title>On this day: December 21</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20211221000000/en"/>
		<updated>2021-12-21T00:00:00Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_21&quot; title=&quot;December 21&quot;&gt;December 21&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_solstice&quot; title=&quot;December solstice&quot;&gt;December solstice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (15:59&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time&quot; title=&quot;Coordinated Universal Time&quot;&gt;UTC&lt;/a&gt;, 2021); &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Yule&quot; title=&quot;Yule&quot;&gt;Yule&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; begins
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 162px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:ToadLane2009.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;The Rochdale Pioneers&amp;#39; first store&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Rochdale Pioneers&amp;#39; first store&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ToadLane2009.jpg/162px-ToadLane2009.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;162&quot; height=&quot;122&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ToadLane2009.jpg/243px-ToadLane2009.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ToadLane2009.jpg/324px-ToadLane2009.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;3664&quot; data-file-height=&quot;2748&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;The Rochdale Pioneers' first store&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1826&quot; title=&quot;1826&quot;&gt;1826&lt;/a&gt; – Settlers from the United States in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mexican_Texas&quot; title=&quot;Mexican Texas&quot;&gt;Mexican Texas&lt;/a&gt; made the first attempt to secede from Mexico, establishing the short-lived &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Fredonian_Rebellion&quot; title=&quot;Fredonian Rebellion&quot;&gt;Republic of Fredonia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1844&quot; title=&quot;1844&quot;&gt;1844&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Rochdale_Society_of_Equitable_Pioneers&quot; title=&quot;Rochdale Society of Equitable Pioneers&quot;&gt;Rochdale Pioneers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; opened their store &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Rochdale&quot; title=&quot;Rochdale&quot;&gt;Rochdale&lt;/a&gt;, England, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/History_of_the_cooperative_movement&quot; title=&quot;History of the cooperative movement&quot;&gt;forming the basis for the modern co-operative movement&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1923&quot; title=&quot;1923&quot;&gt;1923&lt;/a&gt; – Nepal and the United Kingdom signed &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Nepal%E2%80%93Britain_Treaty_of_1923&quot; title=&quot;Nepal–Britain Treaty of 1923&quot;&gt;the first treaty that defined the international status of Nepal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; as an independent and a sovereign nation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1965&quot; title=&quot;1965&quot;&gt;1965&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/United_Nations&quot; title=&quot;United Nations&quot;&gt;United Nations&lt;/a&gt; adopted the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/International_Convention_on_the_Elimination_of_All_Forms_of_Racial_Discrimination&quot; title=&quot;International Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination&quot;&gt;International Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, which 88 member states have since signed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1988&quot; title=&quot;1988&quot;&gt;1988&lt;/a&gt; – The world's largest aircraft, the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Antonov_An-225_Mriya&quot; title=&quot;Antonov An-225 Mriya&quot;&gt;Antonov &lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;An-225&lt;/span&gt; &lt;i&gt;Mriya&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, made its first flight.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hugh,_Margrave_of_Tuscany&quot; title=&quot;Hugh, Margrave of Tuscany&quot;&gt;Hugh, Margrave of Tuscany&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1001)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/William_H._Osborn&quot; title=&quot;William H. Osborn&quot;&gt;William H. Osborn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1820)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Adele_Goldstine&quot; title=&quot;Adele Goldstine&quot;&gt;Adele Goldstine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1920)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
